/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>大家不能掉以輕心</strong><br />\n或者有人認為政府會顧及香港嘅國際環境唔會輕易斷網，但現在中共已經失去理性，當中央黔驢技窮，損害香港利益而徹底封網並非不可。就好似半年前大家都唸唔到香港已經失去遊行以及戴口罩嘅自由。<br />\n<br />\n本文為節錄，全文請到此瀏覽：<br />\n<br />\n（分析+行動）政府有意部署封網，封網後香港變新疆！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1639585\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1639585</a>"},{"pid":"e2980f3d71e3b06f111e70871fc81f0ce46cbb83","tid":1640130,"uid":173002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"24beeef082b8284223b7f3218bc235f12877e83c","tid":1640130,"uid":50423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T01:53:53.000Z","msg":"唔緊要呀 打爛狗鐵我就支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T03:19:16.000Z","msg":"黑警串通黨鐵落閘後縱火燒站係栽贓嫁禍，手段極為污穢，唔可以俾暴政抹黑同分化香港人。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1328a3c4ad2c57dd03be8f55f586dbd0322340ee","tid":1640130,"uid":62247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T03:23:18.000Z","msg":"你用個屎忽諗都知cctvb唔會現場拍攝到啦<br />\n真係企係度比你影咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n出動曬成個傳媒機器拍戲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64e178788c79b6f6ecd605bcf8910f263c25263d","tid":1640130,"uid":180293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T03:24:52.000Z","msg":"其實宜家咁多盤係地鐵附近<br />\n住附近既人裝cam 24小時睇住仲好"},{"pid":"4b62d7f5baf879d29f3cef89249a8dd6e084a294","tid":1640130,"uid":188482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T03:25:50.000Z","msg":"你知 我知 我諗好多人都知 係腦殘藍絲唔撚知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6fc3ee37bf7b66df1a4dbd237d3cf3347e401816","tid":1640130,"uid":268537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T03:27:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7931d479f53f8ce5653450e7c3ccdfc8b85dc79f","tid":1640130,"uid":268537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c2d896c61e98560caec547c0aec21b42f0ceb7